# Ollama runtime settings
# Local .env values are for development only.
# In Docker or CI, set real environment variables instead of editing source code.
# Recommended modern local default:
# - qwen3.5:4b: 3.4GB, 14.7M downloads, strong small general/agentic model
#
# Other local model options under 10GB:
# - qwen3.5:2b: 2.7GB, faster and lighter
# - qwen3.5:9b: 6.6GB, stronger if your machine has enough memory
# - gemma4:e2b: 7.2GB, popular modern multimodal edge model
# - gemma4:e4b: 9.6GB, stronger Gemma 4 edge option
# - ornith:9b: 5.6GB, coding-agent focused model
# - lfm2.5-thinking:1.2b: 731MB, very lightweight thinking model
#
# Install one model locally, for example:
# ollama pull qwen3.5:4b
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen3.5:4b
